title: Chelsea Not Ready
description:
The FC Crew talk Thomas Tuchel saying he cannot guarantee Chelsea will be ready in two weeks. Erling Haaland scores his first goal for Manchester City. Also, the guys discuss Barcelona's 1-0 El-Clasico win over Real Madrid and should Frenkie de Jong play center back for Barca.
